{"parentUuid":"7efa6fd4-3c68-4f88-9fa8-c585c35cbcf7","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01SuQ3yk7kEbveX5EMjgdw85","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_015h8uU7S33pdWhrgvBHPdhP","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/home/nick/repos/serval/docs/plans/2026-03-29-lb-health-findings-fixes.md","old_string":"**Step 1: Write the failing test**\n\nAdd a concurrent write test to `serval-health/tests.zig` that exercises both `recordFailure` and `recordSuccess` from multiple threads simultaneously. This test exercises the exact race pattern: request-path threads calling `recordFailure` while prober-like threads call `recordSuccess` on the same backend.","new_string":"**Step 1: Write concurrent stress test**\n\nAdd a concurrent write stress test to `serval-health/tests.zig` that exercises both `recordFailure` and `recordSuccess` from multiple threads simultaneously. This test exercises the exact race pattern: request-path threads calling `recordFailure` while prober-like threads call `recordSuccess` on the same backend. Note: data races are timing-dependent and may not deterministically fail before the fix; this test documents the concurrent contract and will catch regressions/UB under sanitizers."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6706,"cache_read_input_tokens":71534,"output_tokens":2140,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":6706,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZXjB5dtPJJAhzY3u2BcV","type":"assistant","uuid":"652acec4-244b-43dc-9c90-9a04cecdee36","timestamp":"2026-03-29T17:00:17.867Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/home/nick/repos/serval","sessionId":"646a4f49-bebb-4328-acf0-8f573ea592f5","version":"