{"parentUuid":"37303b8a-0f9b-4694-b76f-b4c1c565f308","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_016uoMnGBiV2FGFLLrQCpFBv","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01GuTxqeiexMioSC9F57ssMM","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/home/nick/repos/serval/docs/plans/2026-03-29-lb-health-findings-fixes.md","old_string":"```zig\n        // Validate TLS context when any upstream requires TLS.\n        // Without client_ctx, TLS probes silently fail and backends stay permanently unhealthy.\n        if (client_ctx == null) {\n            for (upstreams) |upstream| {\n                if (upstream.tls) return LbError.TlsContextRequired;\n            }\n        }\n```","new_string":"```zig\n        // Validate TLS context when probing is enabled and any upstream requires TLS.\n        // Without client_ctx, TLS probes silently fail and backends stay permanently unhealthy.\n        // Only relevant when probing is active — without probing, no TLS handshakes are attempted\n        // by the LbHandler (request-path TLS uses its own client_ctx from the Client).\n        if (lb_config.enable_probing and client_ctx == null) {\n            for (upstreams) |upstream| {\n                if (upstream.tls) return error.TlsContextRequired;\n            }\n        }\n```"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":954,"cache_read_input_tokens":81645,"output_tokens":396,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":954,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZXjH7h5hSK5UoRZZydZp","type":"assistant","uuid":"f3e225d5-4e95-412d-911f-ac2be8493a11","timestamp":"2026-03-29T17:01:01.418Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/home/nick/repos/serval","sessionId":"646